## ğŸ§  AI Quest Logic

> The AI system reads user input (max 5 prompts during onboarding) to:
- Tag user interests
- Generate initial Quests
- Estimate Pomodoro durations per subtask
- Recommend resources if "Follow up with AI" is triggered

